[[file:Gastroscan eng.jpg|thumb|]]
The '''Gastroscan''' is a Russian brand of computer equipment for the diagnostic test of the [[gastrointestinal tract]]: an [[esophageal pH monitoring]], an intragastric pH-metry, [[esophageal motility study]], a [[Electrogastroenterography#Cutaneous_electrogastrography|cutaneous electrogastrography]] and [[Electrogastroenterography#Electrogastroenterography|electrogastroenterography]], an [[impedance-pH monitoring]], an antroduodenal, [[sphincter of Oddi]] and [[anorectal manometry]] and others.<ref name="GS">Functional Gastroenterology, website. [http://www.gastroscan.ru/en/gastroscan/ The diagnostic equipment for functional gastroenterology].</ref><ref name=Tri>{{cite journal |last=Trifonov |first=Mikhail |title=Devices and Probes for Intracavitary pH Monitoring  |journal=Biomedical Engineering |volume=37 |issue=3 |pages=156<U+2013>160 |year=2003 |doi=10.1023/A:1025871231480 |url=http://www.springerlink.com/content/j5g251617jr61618/ }}</ref><ref name=RapLRT>{{cite book |last= Rapoport |first= SI |coauthors= Lakshin AA, Rakitin BV, Trifonov MM |editor = Komarov FI|title= <U+0440><U+041D>-<U+043C><U+0435><U+0442><U+0440><U+0438><U+044F> <U+043F><U+0438><U+0449><U+0435><U+0432><U+043E><U+0434><U+0430> <U+0438> <U+0436><U+0435><U+043B><U+0443><U+0434><U+043A><U+0430> <U+043F><U+0440><U+0438> <U+0437><U+0430><U+0431><U+043E><U+043B><U+0435><U+0432><U+0430><U+043D><U+0438><U+044F><U+0445> <U+0432><U+0435><U+0440><U+0445><U+043D><U+0438><U+0445> <U+043E><U+0442><U+0434><U+0435><U+043B><U+043E><U+0432> <U+043F><U+0438><U+0449><U+0435><U+0432><U+0430><U+0440><U+0438><U+0442><U+0435><U+043B><U+044C><U+043D><U+043E><U+0433><U+043E> <U+0442><U+0440><U+0430><U+043A><U+0442><U+0430> |trans_title = pH-metry of the Esophagus and Stomach in the Upper Digestive Tract Diseases|url = http://www.gastroscan.ru/literature/authors/3321 | publisher= Medpraktika-M |location = Moscow |year= 2005 |month= |pages = 208|language = Russian |isbn= 5-98803-014-9}}</ref> The '''Gastroscan''' and '